{"tid":1933645,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"同確診空少開派對 商台DJ梁子停工","createTime":"2020-03-19T11:54:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-19T12:09:29.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"aa344bc0bd7e0f8a0fbcb51d807cfe71e6316f5c","tid":1933645,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T11:54:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200319/XDZTHXFVO26NJCJYYLKZ2YTHOY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200319%2FXDZTHXFVO26NJCJYYLKZ2YTHOY%2F&d=vBgtTLCpkGvyAljQauEZFRBk8ry%2Bv12G5j1RUyKX8i0%3D&h=fb3ba76c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200319%2FXDZTHXFVO26NJCJYYLKZ2YTHOY%2F&h=7510584e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200319/XDZTHXFVO26NJCJYYLKZ2YTHOY/</a><br />\n<br />\n同確診空少開派對 商台DJ梁子停工<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一名確診武肺的空中少爺，是商台節目《309咤叱．戀咁嚟》及《梁子力學》主持梁子（原名梁子健）的朋友，據知空少在確診前曾跟朋友開派對，梁子是其中之一，不過他因未有病徵，目前接受家居隔離。但據知梁子前日仍有返商台開工，昨日才停工接受隔離，消息傳出後商台內部人心惶惶，有指昨早林海峰主持《在晴朗的一天出發》時，索性帶私家透明膠板開咪，盡人事阻截病菌侵襲。<br />\n<br />\n對於梁子接受家居隔離，森美昨向《蘋果》表示只是在群組中收到通知，但詳情不清楚。而昨午商台始發內部通告通知員工關於梁子隔離一事，公關部回應：「梁子暫不屬於政府強制隔離人士，已於今早自行到診所做檢測，在有測試結果之前，暫時不會回公司工作。」並稱已為直播室、錄音室及辦公室進行消毒及清潔。<br />\n<br />\n採訪：皓騫<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200319/large/1584536738_938e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200319%2Flarge%2F1584536738_938e.jpg&h=ed0592b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n梁子曾與確診空少開派對，因此需接受檢驗及留在家中隔離。互聯網圖片"},{"pid":"e1a133c9179072757ecfe68f08a57dc0541a8eac","tid":1933645,"uid":59699,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T12:00:49.000Z","msg":"GAY?"},{"pid":"76d27701e24dc3bd057a594c503bc70b716e3b50","tid":1933645,"uid":3189,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T12:09:29.000Z","msg":"空少淫亂派對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}